#: src/application.rs:129 data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:93
msgid ""
"Performance and polish pass, focused on Linux phones like the Librem 5. The "
"app starts and switches views noticeably faster on lower-end ARM hardware, "
"and the consequential-action buttons now carry the standard red tint."
msgstr ""

#: src/application.rs:130 data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:95
msgid ""
"Cold start is roughly twice as fast on slow ARM phones; view switches, "
"session start, and session end no longer stall the UI"
msgstr ""

#: src/application.rs:131 data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:96
msgid ""
"Haptic feedback on session end now fires correctly on devices with "
"feedbackd, without the end-sound doubling up"
msgstr ""

#: src/application.rs:132 data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:97
msgid ""
"Stop, Discard, and per-session delete buttons are styled as destructive "
"(red) per the GNOME HIG"
msgstr ""

#: src/application.rs:133 data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:98
msgid ""
"Log view loads 15 sessions per page by default instead of 200, with Load "
"more for older entries"
msgstr ""

